588
00:40:23,060 --> 00:40:25,774
ORION: 21.

589
00:40:25,798 --> 00:40:27,420
TALIESIN: 22.

590
00:40:27,444 --> 00:40:28,541
MATT: D'accord!

591
00:40:28,565 --> 00:40:30,067
MARISHA: Oh c'est parti?

592
00:40:30,091 --> 00:40:31,941
MATT: C'est parti.

