ORION: Oh, besoin de lumière? (fwoosh)

1455
01:28:57,869 --> 01:28:59,586
MARISHA: Oh, bon sang.

1456
01:28:59,610 --> 01:29:01,191
ORION: Oh, est-ce... Désolé.

